quran[8{c,v,t}:
7,23,dono arz karne lagey ke perwar-digaar hum ne apni jaanun par zulmkiya aur agar to hamein nahi bakhshay ga aur hum par reham nahi kere ga to hum tabah ho jayen ge
7,24,( khuda ne ) farmaya ( tum sab bahisht se ) utar jao ( ab se ) tum aik dosray ke dushman ho aur tumahray liye aik waqt ( khaas ) taq zameen par thikana aur ( zindagi ka ) samaan ( kar diya gaya ) hai
7,25,( yani ) farmaya ke isi mein tumhara jeena hoga aur isi mein marna aur isi mein se ( qayamat ko zindah kar ke ) nikalay jao ge
7,26,ae nabi aadam hum ne tum par poshak utari ke tumhara sattar dhanke aur ( tumahray badan ko ) zeenat ( day ) aur ( jo ) parhaiz gari ka libaas ( hai ) woh sab se acha hai. yeh khuda ki nishanain hain taakay log nasihat pakar yn
7,27,ae nabi aadam ( dekhna kahin ) shetan tumhe b_hka nah day jis terhan tumahray maa baap ko ( b_hka kar ) bahisht se nikalwa diya aur un se un ke kapray utarwa diye taakay un ke sattar un ko khol kar dikha day. woh aur is ke bhai tum ko aisi jagah se dekhte rahay hain jahan se tum un ko nahi dekh satke hum ne shaitano ko inhen logon ka Rafeeq car banaya hai jo imaan nahi rakhtay
7,28,aur jab koi be hiyai ka kaam karte hain to kehte hain ke hum ne apne buzurgon ko isi terhan karte dekha hai aur khuda ne bhi hum ko yahi hukum diya hai. keh do khuda be hiyai ke kaam karne ka hargiz hukum nahi deta. bhala tum khuda ki nisbat aisi baat kyun kehte ho jis ka tumhe ilm nahi
7,29,keh do ke mere perwar-digaar ne to insaaf karne ka hukum diya hai. aur yeh ke har namaz ke waqt seedha ( qble ki taraf ) rukhkiya karo aur khaas isi ki ibadat karo aur isi ko poukaro. is ne jis terhan tum ko ibtida mein pedakiya tha isi terhan tum phir peda hogay
7,30,aik fareeq ko to is ne hadaayat di aur aik fareeq par gumraahi saabit hochuki. un logon ne khuda ko chore kar shaitano ko Rafeeq bana liya aur samajte ( yeh ) hain ke hadaayat yab hain
